						"description": "Get all credit applications for a specific affiliate.\n\n**Roles:** AFFILIATE, ANALYST\n\n**Includes:**\n- Application details\n- Risk evaluation (if available)\n- Status history"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			],
			"description": "Credit application lifecycle management.\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Create application (PENDING)\n2. Evaluate application (ANALYST)\n3. Status updates to APPROVED/REJECTED"
